---
title: Classic Christmas Sides Crispy Rosemary Roast Potatoes and Homemade Cauliflower Cheese
description: This year, we’ve made it easy to choose the festive dishes you want, at a time to suit you. These Classic Christmas Sides include the perfect, crispy roast potatoes flavoured with rosemary and an indulgent cauliflower cheese. Pair with a main, add another side to fill the table and select a starter and dessert to finish off your festive feast this Christmas!
